Incidentally, I recently added a function to metafor to facilitate the calculation of the sampling variance of effect sizes from CIs:

https://wviechtb.github.io/metafor/reference/conv.wald.html

Its use is illustrated here:

https://www.metafor-project.org/doku.php/tips:assembling_data_or

The example is based on (log) odds ratios, but the same principle applies to other 'effect sizes'.

Best,
Wolfgang

